81.5	Heston_Blumenthal	Heston Blumenthal	Heston Marc Blumenthal, OBE (born 27 May 1966 in London, raised in Buckinghamshire) is an English chef and owner of The Fat Duck, a three-Michelin-starred restaurant in Bray, Berkshire which has been voted Best Restaurant in the UK and received a perfect score of 10/10 every year since 2007 by The Good Food Guide. Additionally, it was voted best restaurant in the world in 2005 by Restaurant magazine. Since that date, it was awarded 2nd place in 2006, 2007, 2008 and 2009, 3rd in 2010 and 5th in 2011.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/97/Hestonregentspark.jpg/220px-Hestonregentspark.jpg
